snippet.title: Whispering Hills - Epsiode 3 - Releasetrailer
snippet.description:
Download at: https://www.whisperinghills.net  
Whispering Hills  A Silent Hill Horror Mod for Fallout 4

We are proud to announce Whispering Hills Epsiode 3!  
Continue to explore from Epsiode 2 and face your inner fears! The Silent Hill P.T. Section and the Blue Creek Apartments await you. Find out more what happend to this town as the Story progresses!

Find out more about Whispering Hills at: https://www.whisperinghills.net
Support our work at Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/vividian
Join us at Discord: https://discord.gg/2Ht4PDD
